{"tid":408620,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明點解康文署起咁多所謂健身設施係公園度","createTime":"2017-09-21T11:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T14:46:13.000Z","uid":59664,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8866f125cc8536f9fbe044b61bc181ba69b6df7f","tid":408620,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"其實你有引體bar, 雙槓已經好夠<br />\n有埋吊環就最好<br />\n但有好多公園連呢啲基本野都無<br />\n反而起埋一大堆無人用嘅垃圾<br />\n又或者將啲基本嘢起到奇奇怪怪咁, 例如得兩隻手掌闊度嘅引體bar<br />\n我見啲阿伯都係用雙槓,引體bar做運動<br />\n大部份肌肉都練到<br />\n用來拉筋又得<br />\n公園規劃啲人係咪全部都肥佬肥婆嚟㗎<br />\n屌<br />\n越講越嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6dd03f2cdf5ce6c637b20e2b468722be599fae","tid":408620,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"康文署有健身室，洗乜去公園做"},{"pid":"c7d683f00dfed57c420f80bc1721e19c647eec0d","tid":408620,"uid":23141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾三寶<br />\n<br />\n阿婆單車、硬到仆街嘅sit up 板、上下拉繩"},{"pid":"ec20df77e813d9f127b443b3fbb2ba9609ccfea1","tid":408620,"uid":37757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾三寶<br />\n<br />\n阿婆單車、硬到仆街嘅sit up 板、上下拉繩</blockquote><br />\nD SIT UP板仲要比太陽哂完熱到做鐵板燒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bee66471383986d720bdf450a5e153ee0b28743","tid":408620,"uid":4527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"整D高低單杆同雙杆夠哂做真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2169a4adc7d1894256bd87ee157eea88a7ff5b92","tid":408620,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>康文署有健身室，洗乜去公園做</blockquote><br />\n康文署健身室真係不了<br />\n入面舉下鐵都ok嘅"},{"pid":"409f3601633c3bc47ad6ed6b5b3a1a3bb4cfcdb0","tid":408620,"uid":9053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-