<br />\n與其去gym, 我寧願俾多小小玩 crossfit 算"},{"pid":"c190d22207b446599f08b597e9a07565f5711de5","tid":408620,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n官涌同埋大角咀個間真係好大，仲要好平一個月＄90任做，抵阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家玩calisthenic 已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n與其去gym, 我寧願俾多小小玩 crossfit 算</blockquote><br />\n幾錢？好似好辛苦咁"},{"pid":"5704c85fa630733c6e7c31046314b34137486156","tid":408620,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n官涌同埋大角咀個間真係好大，仲要好平一個月＄90任做，抵阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家玩calisthenic 已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n與其去gym, 我寧願俾多小小玩 crossfit 算</blockquote><br />\n幾錢？好似好辛苦咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCalisthenic 其實同街頭健身一樣<br />\n本身唔需要咩工具<br />\n同friend一齊睇youtube片玩都可以進步好快<br />\n健身效果都ok<br />\n但香港唔好話街頭健身公園<br />\n連搵個有引體bar嘅公園都要左搵右搵<br />\n<br />\n所以我自已係屋企都整左個引體架<br />\n加多對吊環, paralletes已經玩晒所有野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/224251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F224251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=977a1611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係帶班friend 玩就要搵地方<br />\n<br />\ncrossfit 上網睇片好似唔錯, 想試, 但係就貴d"}]}